Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paku! Paku...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like you, Izumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall not follow you, woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, mornin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone that I cried yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Who would I tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just promise me you won't tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh shut up, I said I'm not telling anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't been there, who knows what would have happened to Paku and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you washed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a nice person after all! I misjudged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misjudged? I washed it because it was dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Seriously? Was it that dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In two or three days the fever will go down and you can get up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get some rest for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Mr. Okumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Okumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that demon yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're investigating how it got in and where it went right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a higher level Naberius.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say that the Academy is protected by barriers and charms?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I'm really impressed you remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but every now and then such beasts can sneak in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to brace ourselves just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Okumura cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okumura is fabulous too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe that they're really twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'll quit the cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:05:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had been nicer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that this exorcism thing isn't my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll still be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't look like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you the way you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the order of a certain person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain person? Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first I thought it was Satan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't think of any reason why he'd try to get me killed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be those who'll come to hunt you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. If they're targeting me anyway, why not attack me head on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:05:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just pop up like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, don't just sit up like that, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I can do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why are you doing laundry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I want to be of some use, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With stuff only I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all working hard to become Exorcists and help people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you don't want to become an Exorcist?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first let me just do my specialty, laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:07:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of ze demonz 'ave a so called le "fatal verse", words or quotes zat will make zem le die instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aria specializez in le memorization and le recital of zose fatal verses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zen let's 'ear you recitez what I gave youze for 'omework.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiki! What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Umm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ze "Te Deum". Continuez from where we were le last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Every day we thank thee. And we praise... "
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We praise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...praise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yez?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now zat is unusual for you, Mademoiselle Kamiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zen Suguro, 'elp 'er out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day we thank Thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:08:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we praise Thy Name forever, yea, forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O Lord, deign to keep us from sin this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have mercy on us, O Lord, have mercy on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Thy mercy, O Lord, be upon us, for we have hoped in Thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O Lord, in Thee I have hoped; let me never be put to shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zat was le perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! I was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful not to fall for me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really smart after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than being smart, Bon's just good at memorizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konekomaru, that means I'm smart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memorizing isn't that great a skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear that from someone who can't even remember four lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I can't, I just chose not to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aria are totally defenseless while chanting, so they need to be protected by their team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just luggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! We're aiming for Aria, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to hit me, go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't stand you. Don't laugh at people's dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that you'll defeat Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me not to laugh at such a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about you? Why do you want to become an Exorcist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never told anyone why I want to become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike show-offs like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! If you want to fight, do it somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:09:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you behave yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,What's with this stone? It's getting heavier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,It's a low level demon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,It gets heavier... while you hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,You don't even know about Ghost Stones? Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's because you had to pick a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called collective responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another purpose to this camp besides studying,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's strengthening your bonds with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to have any bonds with these people!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to get along with each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Exorcist cannot fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Support each other's abilities and cover the weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone fights in teams of at least two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In actual battles, a quarrel in the team can lead to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll be gone for three hours on a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the incident with the Ghoul yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lock every entrance to the dormitory
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and put up strong barriers around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lock the entrances? Then how can we get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for you to go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the three hours that I'll be gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will get on well and cool your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three hours... he's the demon here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore. Are you two really related?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a really nice guy. Somewhere deep within.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in this nice situation because of a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Says the one who grabbed me by the collar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who started the fight to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight with me in the middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are an annoying woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me something new. So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just scare everyone away like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stone fell on my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? Did he turn the lights off, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then is it a blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, look. There are lights outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this building the only one without power?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shima, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, events like this always make me excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A real test of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I guess I haven't slept enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{CM}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Ghoul from yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he put up barriers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, it's its miasma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something! I have to protect everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ni! Can you give me eely-billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ni!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved us, Shiemi. Thanks to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's lively for a corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ghouls get really active when it's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiemi, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It got so hot suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of the Ghoul's miasma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, Yukio, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Moriyama's strength runs out, the barricade will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll be done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not picking up his phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go out and lure it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it follows me, you guys run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me, I'm stronger than I look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idi{\fscx250}-{\fscx100} hey! Come back, Okumura!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okumura!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're after me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's just get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriyama, you can lower the barricade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Didn't you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lights...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I turn on the lights, the Ghoul will get weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just sit and wait until it gets through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kill it with chants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Bon, that's fine but do you know its fatal verse?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't, but Ghoul type demons usually have their fatal verses from the Gospel of John.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I memorized all of it already, so if I just recite it, I'll hit the right one somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it? That's more than 20 chapters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,21, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I memorized one to ten. Let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, let's do this, Konekomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you start chanting, it'll go and attack you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I cared! A girl is protecting us all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy can't just sit back and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon, you're the real man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't memorized any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you had that with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it gets through, I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You had such a big mouth earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now that things get real you wet yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back if you're not going to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konekomaru, you do it from the first chapter, I'll start from the 11th.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now a certain man was sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the beginning was the Word...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The switchboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all off! If I turn it on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, those flames are what I wanted to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those blue flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you can't use your powers in front of others,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I took the liberty of inviting you here, Okumura Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Son of Satan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let not your heart be troubled: ye believe in God, believe also in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have yet many things to say unto you, but ye cannot bear them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost gotten through!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\a6}...signifying by what death he should glorify God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon has almost reached the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damned thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when he had spoken this, he saith unto him, 'Follow me.'
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was yesterday's incident your doing, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me! Show me that power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he? Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today... you weren't your usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I all right? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon, are you done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't my usual self. She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I humbly call upon the Gods of Harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow my wishes, leave none unfulfilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woman, how dare you summon us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know your pla{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obey me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She broke out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\a6}Then went this saying abroad among the brethren, that that disciple should not die...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four, five...{six, seven, eight, nine, ten...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bad person, but I'm also a sore loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tremble as a leaf, tremble I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall... and never return to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the disciple which testifieth of these things, and wrote these things:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we know that his testimony is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that even the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that even the world itself could not contain the books that should be written!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll di-di-die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there another one here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took it out. You defeated yours, too? Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's wrong with you?! Do you want to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, do you want to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks anyway. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paku... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo... I love you the way you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I seeing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yukio! Where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.87,0:23:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.67,0:24:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.87,0:24:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all to understand Rin Okumura's powers as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.11,0:24:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.78,0:24:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki! Rin!
