Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:14.59,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}kore ga sou "pride" sorezore no basho de
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:18.92,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,717)}mada mada kieru na kokoro no hi wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:24.39,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,mada mada ikeru zo ikeru zo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:11.56,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,After birth, people live as they wish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:14.19,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,They then learn the black box in their head; is that bliss?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:16.74,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Just cross over, beyond the line of your limit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.74,0:01:19.70,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, take a step, and I mean this minute
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:24.99,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Life's a bitch, so if it's easy, you're doing it wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.99,0:01:30.12,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, which way is the world going? Then ignore it and go wherever (here we go)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:34.88,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things I could never have, things with time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:39.47,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a reason I force my heart upon them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:44.95,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I never tried to understand, I just forced it on them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.22,0:01:48.85,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no better than those lifeless adults
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:53.94,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's just a pipe dream I could never have
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:58.44,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one can put out the fire in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:03.70,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The black rain may pour hard and leave me drenched
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:09.12,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know I can change, I will change myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:14.59,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}This is my pride, what makes up my core
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:18.92,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,15)}I won't let my fire be put out; not yet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:24.39,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep going, and I'll never stop
